As explained in my last article, money and surviving the Coronavirus Pandemic are very important "Second Things."
Lewis's "Principle of First and Second Things," if a society only focuses on its very important Second Things, like money and survival, in the end that society does not achieve those Second Things and in the process loses its First Things.